<section class="features-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Powerful features for pros</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to create, optimize, and manage your App Store presence</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
            <path d="m2 17 10 5 10-5"/>
            <path d="m2 12 10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Element Layers</h3>
        <p>Organize your screenshots with powerful layering system. Move, resize, and style elements independently for pixel-perfect control.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/>
            <path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/>
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Loupe Effect</h3>
        <p>Highlight specific UI elements with our signature loupe magnification. Perfect for showcasing detailed features and interactions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 15V6"/>
            <path d="M18.5 18a2.5 2.5 0 1 0 0-5 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0 5Z"/>
            <path d="M12 12H3"/>
            <path d="M16 6H3"/>
            <path d="M12 18H3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>XCStrings Integration</h3>
        <p>Import and export Xcode localization files seamlessly. Keep your screenshots in sync with your app's localization workflow.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="m22 21-3-3"/>
            <path d="m15 12 3 3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Variant Management</h3>
        <p>Create unlimited variations without touching originals. Perfect for A/B testing different messaging, colors, and layouts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Smart Templates</h3>
        <p>Start with professionally designed templates optimized for conversion. Customize colors, fonts, and layouts to match your brand.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 20h9"/>
            <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Batch Processing</h3>
        <p>Apply changes across multiple screenshots at once. Update text, colors, or layouts for entire screenshot sets with one click.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M3 6h18"/>
            <path d="M19 6v14c0 1-1 2-2 2H7c-1 0-2-1-2-2V6"/>
            <path d="M8 6V4c0-1 1-2 2-2h4c-1 0-2 1-2 2v2"/>
            <line x1="10" y1="11" x2="10" y2="17"/>
            <line x1="14" y1="11" x2="14" y2="17"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Version History</h3>
        <p>Never lose your work with automatic version history. Revert to any previous version or compare changes side-by-side.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/>
            <rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1" ry="1"/>
            <path d="m9 14 2 2 4-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Preview & Validate</h3>
        <p>Preview exactly how your screenshots will appear in the App Store. Validate dimensions, text readability, and overall impact.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Team Collaboration</h3>
        <p>Work together with your team. Share projects, leave comments, and maintain brand consistency across all your app marketing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: #fafbfc;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: white;
    border-color: #e5e7eb;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>